WHEN a family
is grieving the loss of a loved one, they don’t expect unnecessary drama. A video of
a family having a quarrel with their neighbours has surfaced on social media. In the
video, a man can be seen dragging a chain while chasing what looks like family
members of the deceased. Following
that, a white woman can be heard saying: “Ja, put it on social media.” The white
neighbour reportedly claimed that the tent was in their yard.  FOR MORE ON THIS STORY, READ TOMORROW'S DAILY SUN.